title: China shows off rising power marking WWII defeat of Japan
text: China shows off rising power marking WWII defeat of Japan By Associated Press | September 3, 2015 @ 1:37 am Chinese female military personnel march during a parade commemorating the 70th anniversary of Japan's surrender during World War II held in front of Tiananmen Gate, in Beijing, Thursday, Sept. 3, 2015. The spectacle involved more than 12,000 troops, 500 pieces of military hardware and 200 aircraft of various types, representing what military officials say is the Chinese military's most cutting-edge technology. (AP Photo/Ng Han Guan)
